to\": 212}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 216, \"to\": 234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite an investment of 1.4 billion euros ($1.5 billion) to prevent sewage leaks into the waterway, the Seine has been causing suspense in the run-up to the opening of the Paris Games on July 26 after repeatedly failing water quality tests.\", \"from\": 254, \"to\": 495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 359, \"end\": 364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999545253, \"rank\": 4.534295086995487e-11, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an investment\", \"from\": 262, \"to\": 275}, {\"ngram\": \"1.4 billion euros\", \"from\": 279, \"to\": 296}, {\"ngram\": \"sewage leaks\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 335}, {\"ngram\": \"the waterway\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 353}, {\"ngram\": \"suspense\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 390}, {\"ngram\": \"the run-up\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 404}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 419}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 438}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 446}, {\"ngram\": \"water quality tests\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But since the beginning of July, with heavy rains finally giving way to sunnier weather, samples have shown the river to be ready for the open-water swimming and triathlon - and for 65-year-old Hidalgo.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 691, \"end\": 698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"score\": 0.9999877448800065, \"rank\": 1.2255270104854274e-05, \"text\": \"Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the beginning\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 528}, {\"ngram\": \"heavy rains\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"way\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 565}, {\"ngram\": \"sunnier weather\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 584}, {\"ngram\": \"samples\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 614}, {\"ngram\": \"the open-water swimming\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 654}, {\"ngram\": \"triathlon\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 668}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"On the eve of the Games, when the Seine will play a key role, this event represents the demonstration of the efforts made by the city and the state to improve the quality of the Seine's waters and the ecological state of the river,\\\" Hidalgo's office said in a statement on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 983, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 736, \"end\": 741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999545253, \"rank\": 4.534295086995487e-11, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 880, \"end\": 885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999545253, \"rank\": 4.534295086995487e-11, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 935, \"end\": 942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"score\": 0.9999877448800065, \"rank\": 1.2255270104854274e-05, \"text\": \"Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the eve\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 712}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 725}, {\"ngram\": \"a key role\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 762}, {\"ngram\": \"this event\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 774}, {\"ngram\": \"the demonstration\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 803}, {\"ngram\": \"the efforts\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 818}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"the state\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"the quality\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 872}, {\"ngram\": \"the ecological state\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 919}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 932}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 971}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 982}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She had originally planned to swim last month, but had to delay because bacteria indicating the presence of faecal matter were found to be sometimes 10 times higher than authorised limits.\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 1173, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bacteria\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1065}, {\"ngram\": \"the presence\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"faecal matter\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1106}, {\"ngram\": \"authorised limits\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her long-awaited dip has sparked jokes and memes on social media, with one viral AI-generated image showing her looking like the wrinkled Dobby character from the Harry Potter films as she emerges from the water.\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1338, \"end\": 1350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\", \"score\": 0.9985900960467962, \"rank\": 0.0014118940558518673, \"text\": \"Harry Potter\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her long-awaited dip\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"jokes\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1213}, {\"ngram\": \"memes\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1239}, {\"ngram\"