 \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are going it above all for environmental reasons\\u2026 I am proud that we have served as an accelerator.\\\"\", \"from\": 3027, \"to\": 3131, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"environmental reasons\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3079}, {\"ngram\": \"an accelerator\", \"from\": 3115, \"to\": 3129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French authorities have invested in new water treatment and storage facilities in and around Paris, as well as ensuring that thousands of homes and canal boats without waste water connections are linked up to the sewerage system.\", \"from\": 3133, \"to\": 3362, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3133, \"end\": 3139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.7119381699148468, \"rank\": 0.38680230868340537, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 3226, \"end\": 3231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.232741475482486e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"new water treatment and storage facilities\", \"from\": 3169, \"to\": 3211}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 3258, \"to\": 3267}, {\"ngram\": \"homes\", \"from\": 3271, \"to\": 3276}, {\"ngram\": \"canal boats\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3292}, {\"ngram\": \"waste water connections\", \"from\": 3301, \"to\": 3324}, {\"ngram\": \"the sewerage system\", \"from\": 3342, \"to\": 3361}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Major storms still overwhelm the Paris underground waste-water network, however, some of which dates back to the 19th century.\", \"from\": 3364, \"to\": 3490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3397, \"end\": 3414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_Underground_(film)\", \"score\": 0.9999922810563983, \"r